A♣3♣7♠4♣10♦8♦Q♠K♥2♠10♠4♦7♣J♣5♥10♥10♣K♣2♣3♥5♦J♠6♠Q♣5♠K♠A♦3♦Q♥8♣6♦9♠8♠4♠9♥A♠6♥5♣2♦7♥8♥9♣6♣7♦A♥J♦Q♦9♦2♥3♠J♥4♥K♦

